Package: rayrender
Type: Package
Title: Build and Raytrace 3D Scenes
Version: 0.3.1
Author: Tyler Morgan-Wall
Maintainer: Tyler Morgan-Wall <tylermw@gmail.com>
Description: A raytracer for spheres, planes, and cubes. Uses a tidy `tibble` input to build scenes. Based off of Peter Shirley's "Ray Tracing in One Weekend" book series.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: 
    Rcpp (>= 1.0.0),
    parallel,
    assertthat,
    tibble,
    magrittr,
    purrr,
    png,
    raster,
    progress,
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppThread, progress
